                  "pageId": 22799,
                  "revisionId": 2644310,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The calculation of reload time using reload speed is: Reload Time = Base Reload Time ÷ (1 + Reload Speed Bonus)"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Tactical Pump",
                  "pageId": 22799,
                  "revisionId": 2644310,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, Tigris ' new reload time with a max-ranked Tactical Pump would be 1.8s / (1 + 60%) = 1.125 s"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Tactical Pump",
                  "pageId": 22799,
                  "revisionId": 2644310,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Sustained DPS is increased by reload speed modifiers at the same rate as magazine size modifiers."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Tactical Pump",
                  "pageId": 22799,
                  "revisionId": 2644310,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Can be combined with Chilling Reload and Seeking Fury for a maximum 115% reload speed bonus, granting an approximate 53.4884% reduction of reload time."
                }
              }
